<br>
We are the only &quot;magic&quot; class in all of midgard that doesn't use Piety, instead we rely on Charisma. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#efe0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/uargonthecrafter.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Argon the Crafter</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Team Skald Participant</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#ff0000>(9/12/02 9:15:17 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=313.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> ok</span><hr size=1> ok, because while randoming High Lord loot, a skald yelled out that he needed some piety item just as much as the healers bidding did. <br>
So that threw me off. I guess he was joking around.<br>
<br>
thanks <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c2a2><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/ukjeld.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kjeld</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Team Skald Contributor</span><br>  Posts: 60<br> <font color=#ff0000>(9/12/02 10:05:36 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=313.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> hmmm</span><hr size=1> What was that item ? The problem with most of darkness falls loot is that the &quot;need before greed&quot; is always a gray area, many of the items have an appeal to different classes for different reasons. It's not because an item has a piety stat on it that the other stas or effects has no interest for melee classes.<br>
<br>
In most raids, the Gauntlets of Nightfyre and the charisma jewel are often requested and rolled by all classes than can wear, although they are imho primarily skald items. Losing the gauntlets to shamans a few time in a row can get pretty aggravating (charisma is useless for seers no ?) <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
PS : piety is useless for skalds. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#efe0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub36.ezboard.com/uthugantelal.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Thugan Telal</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Team Skald Participant</span><br>  Posts: 7<br> <font color=#ff0000>(9/12/02 1:03:10 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub36.ezboard.com/fteamskaldfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=313.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: hmmm</span><hr size=1> i lost on a roll for the 15 charisma 54 hp gem, because warriors rolled to get the hps. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
<br>
That's ok tho, got a Snow Diamond of the Glacier Giant this morning.<br>
<br>
<br>
